http://example.org/msdo#RequiresHumanOverrideReview

msdo:RequiresHumanOverrideReview rdf:type owl:Class .





### 
http://example.org/msdo#RiskProfile

msdo:RiskProfile rdf:type owl:Class ;

                 skos:closeMatch
icps:PatientCharacteristics .





### 
http://example.org/msdo#RouteOfAdministration

msdo:RouteOfAdministration rdf:type owl:Class ;

                          
skos:closeMatch <http://snomed.info/id/284009009> .





###  http://example.org/msdo#Severity

msdo:Severity rdf:type owl:Class ;

              skos:closeMatch
meddra:Severity .





